Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:52.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:57.07,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:01.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:06.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:12.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:24.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:33.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:39.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:49.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.57,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Assembly at the Royal Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I was asleep for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:17.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, how many days were \Nyou planning on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:23.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle was so worried about you \Nthat she kept checking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering what we were \Ngoing to do if he didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that's called being worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.80,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried, too. But I'm glad \Nyou all came back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Getting rest is important, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,because that's how much energy you \Nused up conquering that dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that my goddess,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,my sister Marie, would enjoy \Nlistening to all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about something more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:03.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I only have 3,214 stories stocked up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:07.37,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When exactly are you going \Nto tell her all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:11.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling? Is the hole \Nin your stomach closed up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.30,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fight me now? Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:18.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not completely closed up yet. \NIn fact, my stomach's so empty, I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:23.34,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! The Sheep Cooks made breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! So good! Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. He needs his nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Want a taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, he can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:47.57,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, nice! Your eating form is excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.71,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The Sheep Cooks are delighted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll have some \Nbreakfast and go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.51,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.57,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You finally awake, kid? \NI guess you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, even though you \Nalways come back banged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:21.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Apparently, Magic Knights\NHeadquarters wants a report on the dungeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,so if you can walk, pay them a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A report?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:27.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.86,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there'll be \Nlots of strong guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.62,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:35.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably cause trouble if you went,\Nso you're not going, Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, there's a fighting mission,\Nso go on that with Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.93,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Luck? Are you sure \Nyou're not Grey in disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:52.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.15,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, pick me! I'll go instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.87,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what yummy things \Nawait me in the Noble Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:06.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, there's no way you can go. \NAll you do every day is eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.70,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La... La!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:15.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I have to write a \Nletter to Marie, so I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:19.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. No one asked you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.75,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.26,sign_7691_87_Clover_Kingdom_R,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Kingdom Royal Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:33.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome! It's this huge up close?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Could you calm down? You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.93,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone with Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How long must you keep saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.12,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:58.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello! If it isn't the members \Nof the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's been a week, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to give a report, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Have your wounds completely healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:11.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! My stomach still hurts a little,\Nbut I ate lots and slept lots, so I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.90,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same age as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better because of your \Nmagic, Mimosa. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd she run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:32.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,When you raised your hand, your arm was \Nshorter than expected, and it startled her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.98,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:36.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Yuno, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.20,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.70,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.70,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.76,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:52.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I, um... Whenever I see Asta, \Nmy chest feels tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.56,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day,\Nall I can think about is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.19,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll hate me \Nafter I ran away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why him? He's a peasant, \Nhe's stupid, short, loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I find all those things endearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.62,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And the contrast between that and his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.37,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. That meathead is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Why do I sound so desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.92,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.13,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel anything for that idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are they moaning about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they have a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I believe headquarters is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are things even \Nyou don't know, four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.90,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:54.55,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's apparently content with \Nbeing called "four-eyes" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.78,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He's much nicer to Asta now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:01.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't often get to come to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you to welcome us yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that flashy old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:25.19,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! That's the current \NWizard King, Julius Novachrono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.72,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is the current...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.11,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...Wizard King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well done acquiring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:57.22,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This magic was probably the most \Nimportant relic in that dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.37,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The most important relic! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.23,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.92,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's so excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:14.36,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the rumors about the Wizard King \Nbeing a total magic nerd were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.07,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you try using this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:24.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I think it activated \Nin the dungeon once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.13,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to use it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.68,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.84,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Aw, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:39.22,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Sylph, the Wind Spirit of \Nthe Four Great Attributes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.06,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she's chosen him this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.38,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All I can say for now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:52.31,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,is that this spell will grow with you and, \None day, become an extraordinary power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.53,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:00.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King! My grimoire has \Nsome weird scribbles in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.37,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.88,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Something I can't read at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.03,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even seen this \Nwriting in any documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This thing pops out of it! Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:23.72,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a second anti-magic sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I got mine to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:32.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anti-magic... C-Can I touch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.22,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you?! It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Wizard King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.50,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you can \Nactually swing this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.65,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My magical power... is being absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.83,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You can have this back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.21,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you're able to wield it \Nbecause you have no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:08.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I don't have any magic, sir? \NAnd about my sword that cuts through magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:16.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, you all did \Nsplendidly. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:21.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,U-U-Um, d-d-do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.53,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.95,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...do you become the Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:35.21,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you both want \Nto become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.67,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Any Magic Knight should have that aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You two! It's rude to ask\Nthe Wizard King that directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:47.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The Wizard King must be proud \Nand have the trust of the people—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.77,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:12:02.32,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect others with pride,\Nand the trust of others comes with merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.78,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one thing people \Nwant from the Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Merit that proves they are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.31,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Gain merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:17.04,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Continuously gaining merit is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:21.80,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who can't do that \Ncan never stand at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.51,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:28.29,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Your newbies have very determined eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.33,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,William, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.02,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.32,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually holding a decoration \Nceremony for the Magic Knights who've been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,awarded an outstanding number of stars today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Deco...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Decoration ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:49.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ceremony where we award those who \Nhave done exceptionally well and honor them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I would love for all of you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.77,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:07.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what decoration ceremonies are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:14.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I could never have imagined this happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.37,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.07,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me better results than them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:44.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... let us begin \Nthe decoration ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:56.89,sign_19920_225_Wizard_King_Gran,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(959,1014)}Wizard King\NGrand Magic Knight\NSenior Magic Knight, First~Fifth Class\NIntermediate Magic Knight, First~Fifth Class\NJunior Magic Knight, First Class\NJunior Magic Knight, Second Class\NJunior Magic Knight, Third Class \NJunior Magic Knight, Fourth Class\NJunior Magic Knight, Fifth Class
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:51.40,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights of the Clover Kingdom are given\Nranks to indicate their level of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:56.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The ranks are further divided into sub-ranks,\Nwith the Wizard King at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If knights are awarded a prescribed number
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,of stars in the time before the \Nannual decoration ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:08.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they are given a new rank by the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:15.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With seven stars earned,\NLeopold Vermillion of the Crimson Lion Kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of \NIntermediate Magic Knight, Second Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.18,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You use the same flame \Nmagic as your older brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.30,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain of the Crimson Lion Kings. \NYour power is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.01,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:36.27,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Crimson Lion Kings\N{\fs30}Leopold Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.27,top,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Evil needs no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:41.02,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With six stars earned, Sol Marron \Nof the Blue Rose Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.73,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\NIntermediate Magic Knight, Third Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:51.74,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You're as dynamic as the men,\Nand your creative earth magic is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.97,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But you might be a bit\Ntoo much of a free spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:57.29,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Blue Rose Knights\N{\fs30}Sol Marron
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.29,top,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can tie me down is my sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.87,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:05.38,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With six stars earned,\NSolid Silva of the Silver Eagles,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.41,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\N Intermediate Magic Knight, Third Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.20,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The maneuverability of \Nyour magic is amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:16.91,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,573)}Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Solid Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.17,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but I think you'd be even more amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.21,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,if you stopped showing off your powers\N and cooperated with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.10,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that in mind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:24.65,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With nine stars earned,\NNebra Silva of the Silver Eagles,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\NSenior Magic Knight, Fifth Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:33.96,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The skillful illusions you create \Nwith your mist magic are splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:38.68,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,535)}Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nebra Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:37.56,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you don't play with \Nthe enemy more than necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.82,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,or you might get bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.54,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:48.05,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With seven stars earned,\NHamon Caseus of the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.79,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\NIntermediate Magic Knight, Second Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.05,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Just by looking at you, the enemy \Nwould never expect your glass magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:16:00.08,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,539)}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Hamon Caseus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.46,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and I bet they're completely boggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.45,top,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:07.77,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With eight stars earned,\NShiren Tium of the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.75,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\NIntermediate Magic Knight, First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:16.86,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike your eloquent magic, \Nyou're a very quiet fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:21.83,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(570,1)}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Shiren Tium
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.94,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd be better off if \Nyou spoke your mind more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.83,top,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:27.84,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,With eleven stars earned,\NAlecdora Sandler of the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.53,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you the title of\NSenior Magic Knight, Second Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:36.56,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You amaze me with your \Ndiligence and flexible magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:42.31,sign_21381_243_Member_of_the_Bl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,1)}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Alecdora Sandler
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.24,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You can probably relax a \Nlittle more once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.81,top,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Dawn has earned \Na total of 71 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.86,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,They are the clear leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the rest of the squads do \Ntheir best to not fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.92,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:59.70,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, there's a simple reception \Nset up for you, so go enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.05,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.87,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I've invited some special guests today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.55,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get to know \Neach other very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.27,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.46,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,regarding that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:18.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Something came up, so I have to \Nexcuse myself, but have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.36,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,All those stares are beginning to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to enjoy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:40.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Wizard King \Nentertaining us like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention the Wizard \NKing went off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:57.19,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so bold? You're amazing, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:59.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's just unrefined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.44,top,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,May I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:09.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mimosa, were you eyeing this meat, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:12.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh... Yes, it looks quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.43,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Vulgar peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.74,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the Wizard King \Ninvite such lowborn scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.55,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense any magic from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.12,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Them capturing the dungeon \Nmust've been sheer luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.81,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,The way he eats is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:32.13,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnatural for him to be here. Filthy rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:40.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, listen to them tear into me.\NGood thing I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.58,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's so forgiving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:47.77,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You also have a peasant in your squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:51.69,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,The peasant who's forgotten his place \Nsince everyone fawns over him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.10,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,because of the four-leaf grimoire he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:19:01.78,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I could've handled capturing \Nthat dungeon even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:07.24,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite confident, crimson brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:11.08,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we expect \Nanything from that peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:17.17,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones who embody Lord Vangeance \Nand the Golden Dawn's ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,W-With all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.62,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for you as well, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.67,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you ashamed, being here \Nwith your lack of skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.93,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,And Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:34.19,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were wounded early on \Nin the dungeon and left the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.48,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you're royalty of \Nthe Vermillion line is laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.78,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Mimosa was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:51.00,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. The most useless fool here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.63,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.21,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.14,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:12.81,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even control your magic. \NYou're such an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.62,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,You've basically been exiled \Nfrom the Silva family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:20.36,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you had the nerve \Nto return to the Noble Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nebra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.70,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You got a big head from one achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.86,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here intending to bring\Nshame upon the Silva name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nozel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.38,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.38,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Begone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.88,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,failure that killed our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to run from these jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:06.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd all be amazing \Nsince you were called here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but you're no different from the rest of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:15.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calling us peasants, rats, \Nembarrassments, failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you think we're worthy or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'm going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.42,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.15,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't even be allowed to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.22,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.83,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pile up merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and shut you all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:11.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:21.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:27.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:29.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:35.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:38.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:41.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:53.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:03.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
