Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:21.71,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:25.80,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}My Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:24.27,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,My Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:30.15,main - subtitles,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my magic. It's hex magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:32.45,main - subtitles,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,In the next ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:34.80,main - subtitles,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,you'll blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:36.70,main - subtitles,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's {\i1}Go{\i0}rdon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:40.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're being rude to the senior \Nmembers of the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even apologize with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:51.05,main,klaus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 21:\N"Capital Riot."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 21\N\N{\fs18} Capital Riot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:53.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Making my glasses sparkle is my magic!
